      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4138 - Hammad ibn Uthman narrated from Al-Halabi, and Hammad ibn Isa narrated from Hariz, from Abu Abdillah (as), that he was asked about killing an animal with a stone or a bullet (projectile).\nImam (as) said: \"No, it should not be eaten.\""
        ]
